{"id": 2968, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于如何处理自己的“数字遗产”，你都有过哪些想象？", "description": "如果可以的话，在多年之后，你希望如何处理自己留下来的各种互联网资产？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 0, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201905271335483dJqS7ho6bRziCm1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5861, "title": "关于如何处理自己的“数字遗产”，你都有过哪些想象？", "content": "关于如何处理自己的“数字遗产”，你都有过哪些想象？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345667, "content": "注销/删除帐号或者上锁，不给任何人“挖坟”的机会", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150259bMTZS6spnA8gLD95.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345669, "content": "氪过金花过心思养肥的帐号，还是希望有人继承", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150245r9814qYbNL6dwj2Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345670, "content": "全放在同一个网页里，生成一个可访问的二维码", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150150h4yYOjw2BPLZ5fWe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345671, "content": "一个设置都不要改，原封不动放那儿做个纪念", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150117LJPlyugZDOaT3SM4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345672, "content": "留给跟自己有相同爱好的人继续使用（陌生网友也 OK", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150031xAHRUymaZhX0IwS7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345675, "content": "干脆整理好了卖一部分给别人，还能变个现", "image": "img/option/option/20190527145937OwTCn2HJrpFU1ZLa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345678, "content": "只留下账号表示“我来过”，发布的内容都删掉", "image": "img/option/option/20190527145951LxeRbjCydqwoAmYs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345679, "content": "捐给收藏/研究的第三方机构，发挥点剩余价值", "image": "img/option/option/20190527150518yYlEKNC7eTAUmLWS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345680, "content": "都不要，我有别的打算", "image": "img/option/option/20190527145851hpkoMO0DRg2FyP6z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}